  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together black treacle, orange juice, lime juice, olive oil, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the beef strips to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread the marinated beef strips onto skewers.",
    "Grill the skewers for 10-12 minutes, flipping occasionally.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve on a slate-tile vessel.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
